846c99afbde76165ed08c1a966425/2ef06/pasted-4.png 2448w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/d48846c99afbde76165ed08c1a966425/d9199/pasted-4.png\"\n            alt=\"upload successful\"\n            title=\"upload successful\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Sensor資料視覺化（使用Processing寫成），即時呈現 MPU6050 raw data、換算後的姿態、觸碰開關狀態：\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 960px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/d51a6bd296b1a459687777fc3d1023c8/8ac56/pasted-6.webp 240w,\n/static/d51a6bd296b1a459687777fc3d1023c8/d3be9/pasted-6.webp 480w,\n/static/d51a6bd296b1a459687777fc3d1023c8/e46b2/pasted-6.webp 960w,\n/static/d51a6bd296b1a459687777fc3d1023c8/f992d/pasted-6.webp 1440w,\n/static/d51a6bd296b1a459687777fc3d1023c8/882b9/pasted-6.webp 1920w,\n/static/d51a6bd296b1a459687777fc3d1023c8/14846/pasted-6.webp 3264w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/d51a6bd296b1a459687777fc3d1023c8/8ff5a/pasted-6.png 240w,\n/static/d51a6bd296b1a459687777fc3d1023c8/e85cb/pasted-6.png 480w,\n/static/d51a6bd296b1a459687777fc3d1023c8/d9199/pasted-6.png 960w,\n/static/d51a6bd296b1a459687777fc3d1023c8/07a9c/pasted-6.png 1440w,\n/static/d51a6bd296b1a459687777fc3d1023c8/29114/pasted-6.png 1920w,\n/static/d51a6bd296b1a459687777fc3d1023c8/2a4bc/pasted-6.png 3264w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/d51a6bd296b1a459687777fc3d1023c8/d9199/pasted-6.png\"\n            alt=\"upload successful\"\n            title=\"upload successful\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span></p>\n<h2 id=\"細節解釋\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E7%B4%B0%E7%AF%80%E8%A7%A3%E9%87%8B\" aria-label=\"細節解釋 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>細節解釋</h2>\n<h3 id=\"應用情境\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%87%89%E7%94%A8%E6%83%85%E5%A2%83\" aria-label=\"應用情境 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>應用情境</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>職能治療輔具</li>\n<li>智慧家庭控制</li>\n<li>遊戲控制器</li>\n<li>空氣樂器演奏</li>\n<li>人機介面操作</li>\n<li>…</li>\n